description: This skill provides Alexa the knowledge of how to do your laundry. You can even ask it for laundry tips.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask laundry buddy how do I clean a car seat
Alexa, tell laundry buddy to give me a tip
Alexa, ask laundry buddy how do I wash jeans
name: Laundry Buddy
shortDescription: A skill that provides help when you do laundry.
